fr.epita.iam.business - package fr.epita.iam.business
Provides the classes necessary to implement the different business features of the application.
fr.epita.iam.datamodel - package fr.epita.iam.datamodel
This is the data model package that has the class in which the identity data types and the parameters have been defined.
fr.epita.iam.exceptions - package fr.epita.iam.exceptions
Provides the classes to handle special exceptions e.g data access initialisation exception for serialisation
fr.epita.iam.launcher - package fr.epita.iam.launcher
Provides the main class that will be used to launch the application.
fr.epita.iam.services - package fr.epita.iam.services
Provides the classes necessary to have the different services that can be accessed by other classes.
fr.epita.iam.tests - package fr.epita.iam.tests
Provides the classes that have been used for testing purposes during development.
fr.epita.iam.util - package fr.epita.iam.util
Provides the utility classes that will be used by other methods in the other classes.
